@startuml
actor "Khách hàng" as User
participant "ProfileService" as Frontend
participant "UserController" as Controller
participant "UserServiceImpl" as Service
participant "ICustomerRepository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: 1. Chỉnh sửa thông tin cá nhân
Frontend -> Controller: 2. PUT /api/users/me (UpdateProfileRequest)
Controller -> Service: 3. updateMyProfile(username, request)
Service -> Repo: 4. findByUsername(username)
Service -> Service: 5. Cập nhật các trường không rỗng
Service -> Repo: 6. save(customer)
Service -> Service: 7. return getMyProfile()
Service --> Controller: 8. UserProfileResponse mới
Controller --> Frontend: 9. 200 OK
Frontend -> Frontend: 10. renderProfile() + updateHeaderUI()
Frontend --> User: 11. Thông tin đã được cập nhật
@enduml